DTV Remote Control ECommerce

Target Device 
	Toshiba Regza DTV
	Google TV
	One Seg TV

Customization of AWS SDK for Toshiba REGZA


Ways to Develop Android Web Services Application

Two available wyas i.e.,
1. Professional and businessable way --> AWS Android SDK + AMI Server , Amazon SimpleDb, S3, SNS, SQS  [A]
2. Cheaper but own SDK development way  + AMI(Amazon Machine Image) Servers --->  [B], [C]


[A]. AWS SDK for Android Samples

http://aws.amazon.com/articles/4225549089557252

[B]. Accessing a JAX-WS web service from Android

http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/webservices/library/ws-android/index.html?ca=drs-

[C]. Develop and deploy JAX-WS Web services on WebSphere Application Server Community Edition V2.0

http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/websphere/library/techarticles/0709_gawor/0709_gawor.html


